(230, 1, '2018-04-26 06:34:46', '2018-04-25 22:34:46', '\r\n		\r\n			<div><span><i></i> 2016年12月5日<i>11:30:52</i></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jlsj/11238.html#comments" rel="external nofollow"><i></i> 1 </a></span><span><i></i> 768 views</span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jlsj/javascript:printme()" target="_self" title="打印"><i></i></a></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jlsj/#"><span></span></a></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				<p><img title="发愿茹素念佛 临终往升极乐世界" alt="发愿茹素念佛 临终往升极乐世界" src="http://www.amituofo108.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/AMTf27.jpg" alt5="念南无阿弥陀佛感应往生的故事" width="450" height="291" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>王阿英，浙江定海人，住在上海八仙桥。小时候就患哮喘，一直没有痊愈。</p>\n<p>一九六二年，阿英已六十三岁，得病很危险。除夕，她的女儿雅君跪在<span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jd/264.html" title="观世音" target="_blank">观世音菩萨</a></span>像前，至诚恳祷，企求延长母亲五年寿命，发誓劝母亲吃素<span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/ddks/12006.html" title="念佛" target="_blank">念佛</a></span>。</p>\n<p>这天夜里，雅君梦见一位老妇人，领着她们母女进入一座庙宇。看见殿中人，身穿黄袍，头戴冕旒，如同帝王。老妇人让她们母女往前站。旁边一人，手执黄纸，用毛笔在纸上画几个圆圈。画毕，递与帝王看。王者点头露出喜悦的颜色，将纸交与另一人，转给雅君，并说：“拿去!”于是老妇人送其母女出门，就醒了。恰好是正月初一。</p>\n<p>雅君得梦后，赶到母亲家，将梦告诉阿英，并说：“母亲你的病不碍事，已经加寿五年，但要吃素念佛。”阿英接受女儿的劝告，即发愿茹素念佛，病也逐渐好转。</p>\n<p>正月初七夜，阿英梦见地藏菩萨软语安慰她。从此每日跏趺坐三次，默念佛号。于一九六七年二月一日命终。临终，身无病苦，面含笑容，对雅君说：“是你渡了我。<span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jlsj/" title="阿弥陀佛" target="_blank">阿弥陀佛</a></span>现在来接我，我走了!”说完就去世了。室内异香馥郁，好久才散。当年六十八岁。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>本文仅代表作者的<span><a href="http://zfbd108.com/10469.html" title="学佛" target="_blank">学佛</a></span><span><a href="http://zfbd108.com/10422.html" title="知见" target="_blank">知见</a></span>, 仅供参考，一切以<span><a href="http://zfbd108.com/7301.html" title="佛陀" target="_blank">佛陀</a></span>说法为准。</p>\n<div><div data-a2a-url="http://www.amituofo108.com/jlsj/11238.html" data-a2a-title="发愿茹素念佛 临终往升极乐世界"><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjlsj%2F11238.html&amp;linkname=%E5%8F%91%E6%84%BF%E8%8C%B9%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%B5%E4%BD%9B%20%E4%B8%B4%E7%BB%88%E5%BE%80%E5%8D%87%E6%9E%81%E4%B9%90%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjlsj%2F11238.html&amp;linkname=%E5%8F%91%E6%84%BF%E8%8C%B9%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%B5%E4%BD%9B%20%E4%B8%B4%E7%BB%88%E5%BE%80%E5%8D%87%E6%9E%81%E4%B9%90%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/qzone?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjlsj%2F11238.html&amp;linkname=%E5%8F%91%E6%84%BF%E8%8C%B9%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%B5%E4%BD%9B%20%E4%B8%B4%E7%BB%88%E5%BE%80%E5%8D%87%E6%9E%81%E4%B9%90%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C" title="Qzone" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/sina_weibo?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjlsj%2F11238.html&amp;linkname=%E5%8F%91%E6%84%BF%E8%8C%B9%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%B5%E4%BD%9B%20%E4%B8%B4%E7%BB%88%E5%BE%80%E5%8D%87%E6%9E%81%E4%B9%90%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C" title="Sina Weibo" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/whatsapp?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjlsj%2F11238.html&amp;linkname=%E5%8F%91%E6%84%BF%E8%8C%B9%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%B5%E4%BD%9B%20%E4%B8%B4%E7%BB%88%E5%BE%80%E5%8D%87%E6%9E%81%E4%B9%90%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C" title="WhatsApp" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjlsj%2F11238.html&amp;linkname=%E5%8F%91%E6%84%BF%E8%8C%B9%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%B5%E4%BD%9B%20%E4%B8%B4%E7%BB%88%E5%BE%80%E5%8D%87%E6%9E%81%E4%B9%90%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C" title="Google+" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/douban?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjlsj%2F11238.html&amp;linkname=%E5%8F%91%E6%84%BF%E8%8C%B9%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%B5%E4%BD%9B%20%E4%B