(361, 1, '2018-04-27 05:54:31', '2018-04-26 21:54:31', '\r\n		\r\n			<div><span><i></i> 2016年10月29日<i>15:37:44</i></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/10589.html#respond" rel="external nofollow"><i></i> 发表评论</a></span><span><i></i> 528 views</span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/javascript:printme()" target="_self" title="打印"><i></i></a></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/#"><span></span></a></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				<p><img title="遇空难急念圣号 观音菩萨施无畏" alt="遇空难急念圣号 观音菩萨施无畏" src="http://www.amituofo108.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/timg-1-1.jpg" alt5="" width="580" height="264" /></p>\n<p>一、机毁人安湖北方觉慧居士之夫人，专诚持<span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gyps/" title="大悲咒" target="_blank">大悲咒</a></span>二十余年，民国三十八年冬率子女由四川乘飞机撤退，忽在中途出事，方夫人及子女在惊慌中从空降落，仅受虚惊，并未受伤。而所带衣箱等，均为飞机起火烧毁。来台后，自谓仗持大悲咒能幸免灾劫也。</p>\n<p>二、机障安返民国三十八年六月余至广州就任军法局秘书，七月随局迁重庆，偕内子郑侣梅先乘中航班机，起飞甫半小时，右翼螺旋浆忽生故障，机斜欲坠，急朗念观音圣号，应声旋转，安返广州白云机场，得免坠毁于粤桂边区之万山丛中而殉难。据检查报告：‘机件损伤甚大，即难修复。’次日换梭飞渝，平安到达。</p>\n<p>三、云开安降三十九年二月二日偕内子由海南岛乘军机飞台南午餐，继飞台北，忽天变云迷，不能降落。沿海低飞，正油尽势危，急朗念观音圣号，突云开机升，安降新竹。</p>\n<div><div data-a2a-url="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/10589.html" data-a2a-title="遇空难急念圣号 观音菩萨施无畏"><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F10589.html&amp;linkname=%E9%81%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E6%80%A5%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%A3%E5%8F%B7%20%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E6%96%BD%E6%97%A0%E7%95%8F" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F10589.html&amp;linkname=%E9%81%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E6%80%A5%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%A3%E5%8F%B7%20%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E6%96%BD%E6%97%A0%E7%95%8F" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/qzone?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F10589.html&amp;linkname=%E9%81%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E6%80%A5%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%A3%E5%8F%B7%20%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E6%96%BD%E6%97%A0%E7%95%8F" title="Qzone" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/sina_weibo?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F10589.html&amp;linkname=%E9%81%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E6%80%A5%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%A3%E5%8F%B7%20%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E6%96%BD%E6%97%A0%E7%95%8F" title="Sina Weibo" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/whatsapp?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F10589.html&amp;linkname=%E9%81%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E6%80%A5%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%A3%E5%8F%B7%20%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E6%96%BD%E6%97%A0%E7%95%8F" title="WhatsApp" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F10589.html&amp;linkname=%E9%81%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E6%80%A5%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%A3%E5%8F%B7%20%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E6%96%BD%E6%97%A0%E7%95%8F" title="Google+" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/douban?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F10589.html&amp;linkname=%E9%81%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E6%80%A5%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%A3%E5%8F%B7%20%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E6%96%BD%E6%97%A0%E7%95%8F" title="Douban" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/wechat?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F10589.html&amp;linkname=%E9%81%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E6%80%A5%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%A3%E5%8F%B7%20%E8%A7%82%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E6%96%BD%E6%97%A0%E7%95%8F" title="WeChat" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a rel="external nofollow" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share"></a></div></div>							</div>\r\n\r\n						\r\n									\r\n						\r\n				\r\n									<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span>\r\n			<a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/javascri