r>\r\n\r\n				<div></div>\r\n	<p><b>该文章由WP-AutoPost插件自动采集发布</b></p><p><b>原文地址:<a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gyps/11062.html">http://www.amituofo108.com/gyps/11062.html</a></b></p>', '观音菩萨加持我 唱出六字大明咒狮子吼 警醒众人要好好学佛修行', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e8%a7%82%e9%9f%b3%e8%8f%a9%e8%90%a8%e5%8a%a0%e6%8c%81%e6%88%91-%e5%94%b1%e5%87%ba%e5%85%ad%e5%ad%97%e5%a4%a7%e6%98%8e%e5%92%92%e7%8b%ae%e5%ad%90%e5%90%bc-%e8%ad%a6%e9%86%92%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e8%a6%81', '', '', '2018-04-27 11:15:07', '2018-04-27 03:15:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/archives/375', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(376, 1, '2018-04-27 04:15:11', '2018-04-26 20:15:11', '\r\n		\r\n			<div><span><i></i> 2016年11月22日<i>09:39:48</i></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/239.html#respond" rel="external nofollow"><i></i> 发表评论</a></span><span><i></i> 378 views</span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/javascript:printme()" target="_self" title="打印"><i></i></a></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/#"><span></span></a></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				<p><img title="观世音菩萨灵感记两则" alt="观世音菩萨灵感记两则" src="http://www.amituofo108.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/35bf65207aa79e8eef71b9923ff8d5b5.jpg" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>《妙法莲花经<span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jd/264.html" title="观世音" target="_blank">观世音菩萨</a></span><span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jd/264.html" title="普门品" target="_blank">普门品</a></span>》:</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>"无垢清静光慧日破诸暗<br />\n能伏灾风火普明照世间"</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>◆晋朝有位姓徐单名叫荣的，是山东省琅琊县人，时常到东阳去，回来的时候，经过定山，架船的人不习于水道，误堕洄流水中，垂垂将要沉没，荣那是也无有其他好计策可想。惟有至心诚意称念观世音名号，不一会，好像有几十人来一齐用力将船拖出洄流，沿著江水而下，暮色已晚，天昏地暗，风雨交加，向前驶去，不知所向何处呢，风浪更大船几乎要翻了，荣更加至诚诵<span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/ddks/12006.html" title="念佛" target="_blank">念佛</a></span>经不停，忽然的望见山头火光透亮，于是船向著火光行去，安然的到达岸边，既而登到岸上，即不再见有火光了，明日清晨，荣向浦中的人询问，昨夜山上是什么火光了，大众都很惊异的说，作业风雨如此之大，那见什么火光呢?于是才知道是佛力的保佑!荣后来为稽的督护官，有名士叫谢敷的时常讲述这件事，和荣同船的人有个之道蕴和尚，是位谨慎笃实的人，也将这件事的发现自始至终对一位传亮谈及，和荣所说的情况完全相同。(冥详记)</p>\n<p>◆晋朝有个和尚叫竺法纯，居住在山阴地方的显义寺里，元兴年间，行船经过太湖，忽然遇到了暴风，船小进了水，命在旦夕，于是一心一意凭依著观世音，口不停的诵念圣号，忽然有只大船漂流到船前面，因此共扳舷而上，大众方将度完，回头来看小船当时沉没，而大船随波逐流，一会抵岸，访问船主无人，一转瞬间，大船也不见了。和尚和同船的人皆叹为神的感应。(高僧传初集及法苑珠林)</p>\n<div><div data-a2a-url="http://www.amituofo108.com/gysj/239.html" data-a2a-title="观世音菩萨灵感记两则"><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F239.html&amp;linkname=%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F239.html&amp;linkname=%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/qzone?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F239.html&amp;linkname=%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99" title="Qzone" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/sina_weibo?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F239.html&amp;linkname=%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99" title="Sina Weibo" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/whatsapp?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F239.html&amp;linkname=%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99" title="WhatsApp" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F239.html&amp;linkname=%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99" title="Google+" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/douban?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F239.html&amp;linkname=%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99" title="Douban" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/wechat?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fgysj%2F239.html&amp;linkname=%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%96%E9%9F%B3%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E7%81%B5%E6%84%9F%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99" title="WeChat" 