(390, 1, '2018-04-27 07:56:30', '2018-04-26 23:56:30', '\r\n		\r\n			<div><span><i></i> 2016年10月30日<i>13:57:00</i></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/12207.html#comments" rel="external nofollow"><i></i> 1 </a></span><span><i></i> 422 views</span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/javascript:printme()" target="_self" title="打印"><i></i></a></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/#"><span></span></a></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				<p><img title="小狗为主舍身，主人不离不弃" alt="小狗为主舍身，主人不离不弃" src="http://www.amituofo108.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/bb6fb4f92060eecb4b82c619b37a53b2.jpg" alt5="小狗为主舍身，主人不离不弃.jpg" width="450" height="234" /></p>\n<p>一只名叫Kabang的混血牧羊犬为了救自己的小主人，舍身挡住了飞驰而来的摩托车，整个面部被撕裂，身受重伤。</p>\n<p>但深爱Kabang的主人坚持为它治疗。现在，这只顽强的小狗不仅活下来了，还被当成了大英雄，受到无数人的关爱。</p>\n<p>9岁的Dina Bunggal 和她3岁表妹正横穿一条车来人往的大马路，没注意旁边一辆摩托车飞驰而来，千钧一发之际，Kabang不知从哪里跑了出来，用自己的身体护住了两个小孩。</p>\n<p>结果，Dina和表妹毫发无损，而Kabang面部却受到重创，嘴部以上一片血肉模糊，那英勇的一跃让它的鼻子卡在了摩托车的轮下，而翻倒的车削下了她整个鼻子和下巴。</p>\n<p>Dina的父亲Bunggal 就在附近商店工作，目击了车祸的全过程，当他飞奔赶过去查看Kabang的伤情时，这个小家伙却跌跌撞撞地爬了起来，很快就跑走不知哪去了。两个星期过去，就在大家都以为Kabang伤势过重已经不治身亡时，它又奇迹般地出现在了主人家门口。</p>\n<p>Bunggal和妻子非常感激Kabang英勇救主的行为，断然拒绝了当地宠物医院要为她实施安乐死的提议，一直坚持为Kabang治疗。</p>\n<p>据Bunggal和他的妻子介绍，几年以前，他们把还是只流浪小狗的Kabang抱回了家，一直当成家庭的一员。Kabang和他们的儿子从小一起长大，甚至在一张小床上睡觉，感情非常深厚。Bunggal认为，正是这种如同亲人般的深情厚谊，让Kabang在危急关头毫不犹豫地冲了出来。</p>\n<p>为Kabang诊疗医师AntonLim 表示，Kabang正在逐渐适应身体的状况，恢复情况良好，现在，还育有六只健康的小宝宝。</p>\n<p>小狗为主舍身，主人不离不弃，演绎了一场人与动物的和谐感人画面。</p>\n<div><div data-a2a-url="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/12207.html" data-a2a-title="小狗为主舍身，主人不离不弃"><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12207.html&amp;linkname=%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%8D%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%83" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12207.html&amp;linkname=%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%8D%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%83" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/qzone?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12207.html&amp;linkname=%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%8D%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%83" title="Qzone" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/sina_weibo?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12207.html&amp;linkname=%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%8D%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%83" title="Sina Weibo" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/whatsapp?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12207.html&amp;linkname=%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%8D%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%83" title="WhatsApp" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12207.html&amp;linkname=%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%8D%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%83" title="Google+" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/douban?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12207.html&amp;linkname=%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%8D%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%83" title="Douban" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/wechat?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12207.html&amp;linkname=%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%8D%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%83" title="WeChat" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><