><div>所属分类：<a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/" rel="category tag">戒杀放生</a></div></div>			</footer>\r\n\r\n				<div></div>\r\n	<p><b>该文章由WP-AutoPost插件自动采集发布</b></p><p><b>原文地址:<a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/12902.html">http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/12902.html</a></b></p>', '我们要学会慈悲众生  戒杀放生', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac%e8%a6%81%e5%ad%a6%e4%bc%9a%e6%85%88%e6%82%b2%e4%bc%97%e7%94%9f-%e6%88%92%e6%9d%80%e6%94%be%e7%94%9f', '', '', '2018-04-27 08:36:49', '2018-04-27 00:36:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/archives/397', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(398, 1, '2018-04-27 09:36:45', '2018-04-27 01:36:45', '\r\n		\r\n			<div><span><i></i> 2016年12月13日<i>12:28:48</i></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/186.html#respond" rel="external nofollow"><i></i> 发表评论</a></span><span><i></i> 552 views</span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/javascript:printme()" target="_self" title="打印"><i></i></a></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/#"><span></span></a></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				<p><img title="老和尚讲述出家前的一次打猎经历" alt="老和尚讲述出家前的一次打猎经历" src="http://www.amituofo108.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/f7aa96208100cf4a8c821fd54fcc8287.jpg" /></p>\n<p>有一位六十五岁的老和尚，讲述自己年轻未出家时一次打猎的经历：</p>\n<p>一九七八年，我在四川松潘县以种植草药和打猎为生。有一天，我们一行三人背着猎枪带着猎狗，来到一片树林里，看到树上有一群金丝猴，我们便急不及待地开枪射击。猴子惊恐万分，但因为树下有猎狗，而无法逃脱。有的猴子在树上就被枪杀了，有的被枪打中了没死，跌下来被猎狗咬死。<strong>我看见一只母猴背着一只小猴，正准备对牠射击时，只见那母猴将小猴放到一边，然后用手指一指小猴，又向我摆一摆手，再指一指牠自己。我明白了，那母猴示意不要射小猴，可以射母猴自己。</strong>我被母猴的行为感动了，放下了猎枪。晚上同伴煮猴子肉，我回想起刚才的情景就不想吃，只是内心不断谴责自己，为什么呢？为了吃猴肉，卖猴子皮和骨头，就如此残忍地<span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/xfxx/465.html" title="杀生" target="_blank">杀生</a></span>害命。哎，罪过！罪过！</p>\n<p>老和尚悔恨地说，我的子女都不孝顺，我是被子女从家里赶出来的，这大概是年轻时打猎的果报吧。</p>\n<p>老和尚年轻未出家前打猎，见母猴保护小猴的行为而能放下猎枪，说明他是有善根的人。但愿天下所有猎人都能放下猎枪。</p>\n<div><div data-a2a-url="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/186.html" data-a2a-title="老和尚讲述出家前的一次打猎经历"><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F186.html&amp;linkname=%E8%80%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%93%E7%8C%8E%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F186.html&amp;linkname=%E8%80%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%93%E7%8C%8E%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/qzone?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F186.html&amp;linkname=%E8%80%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%93%E7%8C%8E%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86" title="Qzone" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/sina_weibo?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F186.html&amp;linkname=%E8%80%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%93%E7%8C%8E%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86" title="Sina Weibo" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/whatsapp?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F186.html&amp;linkname=%E8%80%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%93%E7%8C%8E%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86" title="WhatsApp" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F186.html&amp;linkname=%E8%80%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%93%E7%8C%8E%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86" title="Google+" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/douban?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F186.html&amp;linkname=%E8%80%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%93%E7%8C%8E%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86" title="Douban" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/wechat?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F186.html&amp;linkname=%E8%80%81%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%89%93%E7%8C%8E%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86" title="WeChat" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a rel="external nofollow" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share"></a></div></div>							</d