(403, 1, '2018-04-27 04:58:39', '2018-04-26 20:58:39', '\r\n		\r\n			<div><span><i></i> 2016年6月16日<i>16:56:59</i></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/11510.html#respond" rel="external nofollow"><i></i> 发表评论</a></span><span><i></i> 780 views</span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/javascript:printme()" target="_self" title="打印"><i></i></a></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/#"><span></span></a></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				<p><img title="钓鱼，残忍的雅致" alt="钓鱼，残忍的雅致" src="http://www.amituofo108.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/dec16476d396bfd39c8c6d67116c66f9.jpg" alt4="钓鱼，残忍的雅致.jpg" width="474" height="295" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>佛子们，尽量劝别人不要钓鱼。曾几何时，钓鱼，一直被当成修心养性有益健康的活动。从“姜太公钓鱼愿者上钩”到“孤舟蓑笠翁，独钓寒江雪”，钓鱼，被加进了许多的其他元素，使得这一活动好像有了一点诗意，有了一点雅致的感觉。甚至有了一点超凡脱俗。</p>\n<p>于是平民钓鱼，也许纯粹为了改善生活。</p>\n<p>达官贵人爱好钓鱼，为了享受悠闲。</p>\n<p>文人雅士也来钓鱼，据说是陶冶情操。</p>\n<p>我小时候也喜欢钓鱼，喜欢那一分宁静，喜欢鱼上钩时那种沉着的激动，喜欢将鱼儿快速甩出水面的那一份沉甸甸。</p>\n<p>然而，我有幸成为了佛弟子。我仍然喜欢宁静，喜欢那种沉着的激动，喜欢收获的沉甸甸，但我不再喜欢钓鱼。我为我曾经的钓鱼感到无比的惭愧，为曾经建立在鱼儿们极度痛苦上的快乐而感到罪业深重。</p>\n<p>水中是鱼儿们的世界。鱼儿在水中悠闲的觅食。当快乐的小鱼儿一口咬上人们精心设计的诱饵时，对于它来说，灭顶之灾已经开始了，锋利的鱼钩长有倒刺，深深的扎进鱼的上颚或下颚里，甚至被吞进肚子里，随着钓鱼杆的猛烈甩动，生生的将小鱼儿抽将出水面，然后被钓鱼者狠命的将鱼钩拉出，带有鱼嘴里的血，或者带有被拉出的鱼肠子。鱼儿们在无法表达的极度痛苦中，躺在鱼篓里，直至夕阳西下，钓鱼者带着一脸的满足，迎着金色的晚霞，回到家中，鱼儿被活活的刮去鱼鳞，然后生生的开膛破肚，在阵阵抽搐中去尽内脏，最后在滚烫的油锅里崩几下，才能得以暂时<span><a href="http://zfbd108.com/8051.html" title="解脱" target="_blank">解脱</a></span>。</p>\n<p>钓鱼，残忍的雅致。</p>\n<div><div data-a2a-url="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/11510.html" data-a2a-title="钓鱼，残忍的雅致"><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F11510.html&amp;linkname=%E9%92%93%E9%B1%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%BF%8D%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%85%E8%87%B4" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F11510.html&amp;linkname=%E9%92%93%E9%B1%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%BF%8D%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%85%E8%87%B4" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/qzone?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F11510.html&amp;linkname=%E9%92%93%E9%B1%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%BF%8D%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%85%E8%87%B4" title="Qzone" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/sina_weibo?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F11510.html&amp;linkname=%E9%92%93%E9%B1%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%BF%8D%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%85%E8%87%B4" title="Sina Weibo" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/whatsapp?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F11510.html&amp;linkname=%E9%92%93%E9%B1%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%BF%8D%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%85%E8%87%B4" title="WhatsApp" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F11510.html&amp;linkname=%E9%92%93%E9%B1%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%BF%8D%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%85%E8%87%B4" title="Google+" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/douban?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F11510.html&amp;linkname=%E9%92%93%E9%B1%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%BF%8D%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%85%E8%87%B4" title="Douban" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/wechat?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F11510.html&amp;linkname=%E9%92%93%E9%B1%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%AE%8B%E5%BF%8D%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%85%E8%87%B4" title="WeChat" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a rel="external nofollow" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share"></a></div></div>							</div>\r\n\r\n						\r\n									\r\n						\r\n				\r\n									<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span>\r\n			<a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/javascript:;" data-action="ding" data-id="11510" title="点赞"><i></i>赞 <i>\r\n				5</i>\r\n			</a>\r\n		</span>\r\n		<div>\r\n			<div><span></span></div>\r\n							<span data-t