xin" onclick="return false;" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/#"></a></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>		</div>\r\n		<div></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>				\r\n				\r\n			<footer>\r\n				<ul><li>A+</li></ul><div><div>所属分类：<a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/" rel="category tag">戒杀放生</a></div></div>			</footer>\r\n\r\n				<div></div>\r\n	<p><b>该文章由WP-AutoPost插件自动采集发布</b></p><p><b>原文地址:<a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/12554.html">http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/12554.html</a></b></p>', '二十载光阴假修行，得遇佛法开示走出不杀生的误区', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e4%ba%8c%e5%8d%81%e8%bd%bd%e5%85%89%e9%98%b4%e5%81%87%e4%bf%ae%e8%a1%8c%ef%bc%8c%e5%be%97%e9%81%87%e4%bd%9b%e6%b3%95%e5%bc%80%e7%a4%ba%e8%b5%b0%e5%87%ba%e4%b8%8d%e6%9d%80%e7%94%9f%e7%9a%84%e8%af%af', '', '', '2018-04-27 09:16:32', '2018-04-27 01:16:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/archives/417', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(418, 1, '2018-04-27 10:10:32', '2018-04-27 02:10:32', '\r\n		\r\n			<div><span><i></i> 2016年9月20日<i>08:59:41</i></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/12211.html#comments" rel="external nofollow"><i></i> 2</a></span><span><i></i> 732 views</span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/javascript:printme()" target="_self" title="打印"><i></i></a></span><span><a href="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/#"><span></span></a></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				<p><img title="自从放生后，我的人生顺遂了很多" alt="自从放生后，我的人生顺遂了很多" src="http://www.amituofo108.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/a0bbcb2cc122edd8f1884ab41086c85a.png" /></p>\n<p>从<span><a rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.amituofo108.com/ddks/284.html" title="放生" target="_blank">放生</a></span>中所获得的益处，我在此之前也曾或多或少地提到过。可到现在为止，我从中获得的益处已远超过去了。借此机会，我不妨向大家说明一下。</p>\n<p>放生得子。有一次，我无意中从《放生手册》中得知放生能得子。于是，我就半信半疑地去做了。究竟能否得子对于我来说是个未知数。我倒觉得试试无妨。只要有机会去菜市场，我就会买一些鱼虾螺蚌之类的去河边放生。每当放生后，我心里就觉得特别畅快，如释重负。皇天不负有心人。婚后不久，我的妻子便生下了一个胖小子。当时，我真觉得这事有点不可思议，还以为这是一场梦。目前，我儿子就读小学一年级，在班上成绩名列前茅。</p>\n<p>放生愈疾。前些日子，我母亲突发脑血栓。她的血压高的惊人，差点没把脑血管挤破。幸亏送医院及时，我母亲才算保住了性命。在医院住了一月有余，我母亲才下得床。医生说我母亲弄不好就有瘫痪的可能。后来，我得知放生对治疗人的疾病有好处，便很想尝试一下。每次买了鱼虾螺蚌在河边放生时，我就默默地许愿——希望母亲的病能早日康复。治疗与放生相配合，其疗效很显著。半年之后，我母亲不仅没瘫，而且出人意料地快速康复了。如今，我母亲不但行走自如，而且还能做一些力所能及的家务活。你觉得这神不神奇。</p>\n<p>总之，自从放生后，我的人生顺遂了很多。如意之事是接踵而来，先前的多苦多难不再缠绕着我。我觉得这是上天有好生之德给我的极大奖赏。</p>\n<div><div data-a2a-url="http://www.amituofo108.com/jsfs/12211.html" data-a2a-title="自从放生后，我的人生顺遂了很多"><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12211.html&amp;linkname=%E8%87%AA%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%BA%E9%81%82%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12211.html&amp;linkname=%E8%87%AA%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%BA%E9%81%82%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/qzone?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12211.html&amp;linkname=%E8%87%AA%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%BA%E9%81%82%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A" title="Qzone" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/sina_weibo?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12211.html&amp;linkname=%E8%87%AA%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%BA%E9%81%82%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A" title="Sina Weibo" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/whatsapp?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12211.html&amp;linkname=%E8%87%AA%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%BA%E9%81%82%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A" title="WhatsApp" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12211.html&amp;linkname=%E8%87%AA%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%BA%E9%81%82%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A" title="Google+" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/douban?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12211.html&amp;linkname=%E8%87%AA%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%BA%E9%81%82%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A" title="Douban" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/wechat?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amituofo108.com%2Fjsfs%2F12211.html&amp;linkname=%E8%87%AA%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%A1%BA%E9%81%82%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A" title="WeChat" rel="nofollow